Ing '''tayum''' o '''tayung'''  (''Indigofera suffruticosa''), a maki karaniwang lagyung  '''Añil''', '''Guatemalan indigo''', '''Small-leaved indigo''' (Sierra Leone), '''West Indian indigo''', and '''Wild indigo''' king Ingles ampong '''Añil''' king Castila, <ref>http://www.plantnames.unimelb.edu.au/Sorting/Indigofera.html</ref> metung yang  [[tanaman a manyampaga]] (''flowering plant'') king familiang [[Fabaceae]], ing familia ning gisantis.

Katutubu ya ing malisangan bagya (''subtropical'') ampong malisangan (''tropical'') a dake ding [[Americas]], kayabe ya ing [[mauli]] nang dake ning [[Estados Unidos]],  [[Mexico]], [[Kalibudtang America]] (''Central America''), ampong [[Mauling America]] angga king [[pangulu]]ng  [[Argentina]]. Midala ne kareng dakal a dake ning yatu, at ngeni maki leparan yang [[pantropical]] o kareng anggang lugal a malisangan o ''tropical''.<ref name="GRIN"/>  Metung yang matulid a [[palungpung]] a manyanga a miraras {{convert|1|m|ft|abbr=on}} katas a maki [[bulung]] a katabas pakpak (''pinnate''). Tutubu ya kareng malanging lugal a megulu, medistorbu o pikyalman ning tau, alimbawa deng lele dalan o asikan a e mitatamnan.

[[Image:semillas_anil.jpg|thumbnail|right|thumb|Deng butul ning of tayum]]
[[Image:hojas_anil.jpg|thumbnail|right|thumb|Deng bulung ning tayum]]

Maralas deng gagamitan ing tayum king tinang indigo, at nung isamut ya kareng partikular a uri ning pila (''clay'') malyaring gawang [[Maya Blue]] o Azul Maya, a pangule o pangulor a gagamitan da kareng sibilisasyung [[Mesoamerica]]nu.

